         <abstract id="aspace_f3643c8f3ecaae7454e4476df2b49de4">Records of the Epsilon Chapter (Yale University) of Delta Omega, an honorary public health society founded in 1924. Yale's chapter, established in 1925, was organized through the Department of Public Health.</abstract>
